The paper deals with modeling and analyzing cellular networks in fading environments, which is a common topic in the field of information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also presents a tractable model for capturing diverse fading channels, which involves system modeling and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the effect of fading on spectral efficiency, which is a common topic in multimedia systems (cs.MM) and communication networks (cs.COM).
